sequenceDiagram
    participant App
    participant BM as BootManager
    participant DI as Discoverer
    participant CO as ComposeOrchestrator
    participant HC as HealthChecker
    participant EB as EventBus

    App->>BM: BootAll(ctx)
    BM->>EB: Publish(BootStarted)

    Note over BM: Phase 1: Discovery
    loop For each discoverable endpoint
        BM->>DI: Discover(ctx, endpoint)
        DI-->>BM: discovered=true/false
    end

    Note over BM: Phase 2: Group by Compose
    BM->>BM: GroupByCompose(endpoints)

    Note over BM: Phase 3: Start Services
    loop For each compose group
        BM->>CO: Up(ctx, project)
        CO-->>BM: ok/error
        BM->>EB: Publish(ContainerStarted)
    end

    Note over BM: Phase 4: Health Check
    loop For each enabled endpoint
        BM->>HC: CheckWithRetry(ctx, target)
        HC-->>BM: HealthResult
        alt Required + Failed
            BM->>EB: Publish(ContainerFailed)
        else Healthy
            BM->>EB: Publish(HealthChanged)
        end
    end

    BM->>EB: Publish(BootCompleted)
    BM-->>App: BootSummary / error
